      &nbsp;<br>
      a.  the demand curve is relatively steep than if the demand curve is 
      relatively flat. <br>
      b. the demand curve is relatively flat than if the demand curve is 
      relatively steep. <br>
      c. the demand curve is horizontal than if the demand curve is vertical.
      <br>
      d. the demand curve is horizontal than if the demand curve is downward 
      sloping. <br>
&nbsp;</TD></TR>


