      &nbsp;<b>2)</b> 
      The change in price that results from a rightward shift in demand will be 
      greater if<br>
      &nbsp;<br>
      a. the supply curve is horizontal than if the supply curve is upward 
      sloping.<br>
      b.  the supply curve is relatively steep than if the supply curve is 
      relatively flat.<br>
      c. the supply curve is upward sloping than if the supply curve is 
      vertical.<br>
      d. the supply curve is horizontal than if the supply curve is vertical.<br>
&nbsp;</TD></TR>


